{"tha-ap394:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap394:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap394:0.3":"Selattheraapadana ","tha-ap394:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap394:1.2":"vithisami ahosaham; ","tha-ap394:1.3":"Mama nati samanetva, ","tha-ap394:1.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap394:2.1":"‘Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap394:2.2":"punnakkhetto anuttaro; ","tha-ap394:2.3":"Asi so sabbalokassa, ","tha-ap394:2.4":"ahutinam patiggaho. ","tha-ap394:3.1":"Khattiya negama ceva, ","tha-ap394:3.2":"mahasala ca brahmana; ","tha-ap394:3.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","tha-ap394:3.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:4.1":"Hattharoha anikattha, ","tha-ap394:4.2":"rathika pattikaraka; ","tha-ap394:4.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","tha-ap394:4.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:5.1":"Ugga ca rajaputta ca, ","tha-ap394:5.2":"vesiyana ca brahmana; ","tha-ap394:5.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","tha-ap394:5.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:6.1":"Alarika kappaka ca, ","tha-ap394:6.2":"nhapaka malakaraka; ","tha-ap394:6.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","tha-ap394:6.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:7.1":"Rajaka pesakara ca, ","tha-ap394:7.2":"cammakara ca nhapita; ","tha-ap394:7.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","tha-ap394:7.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:8.1":"Usukara bhamakara, ","tha-ap394:8.2":"cammakara ca tacchaka; ","tha-ap394:8.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","tha-ap394:8.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:9.1":"Kammara sonnakara ca, ","tha-ap394:9.2":"tipulohakara tatha; ","tha-ap394:9.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","tha-ap394:9.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:10.1":"Bhataka cetaka ceva, ","tha-ap394:10.2":"dasakammakara bahu; ","tha-ap394:10.3":"Yathasakena thamena, ","tha-ap394:10.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:11.1":"Udahara katthahara, ","tha-ap394:11.2":"kassaka tinaharaka; ","tha-ap394:11.3":"Yathasakena thamena, ","tha-ap394:11.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:12.1":"Pupphika malika ceva, ","tha-ap394:12.2":"pannika phalaharaka; ","tha-ap394:12.3":"Yathasakena thamena, ","tha-ap394:12.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:13.1":"Ganika kumbhadasi ca, ","tha-ap394:13.2":"puvika macchikapi ca; ","tha-ap394:13.3":"Yathasakena thamena, ","tha-ap394:13.4":"pugadhammam akamsu te. ","tha-ap394:14.1":"Etha sabbe samagantva, ","tha-ap394:14.2":"ganam bandhama ekato; ","tha-ap394:14.3":"Adhikaram karissama, ","tha-ap394:14.4":"punnakkhette anuttare’. ","tha-ap394:15.1":"Te me sutvana vacanam, ","tha-ap394:15.2":"ganam bandhimsu tavade; ","tha-ap394:15.3":"‘Upatthanasalam sukatam, ","tha-ap394:15.4":"bhikkhusanghassa karayum’. ","tha-ap394:16.1":"Nitthapetvana tam salam, ","tha-ap394:16.2":"udaggo tutthamanaso; ","tha-ap394:16.3":"Pareto tehi sabbehi, ","tha-ap394:16.4":"sambuddhamupasankamim. ","tha-ap394:17.1":"Upasankamma sambuddham, ","tha-ap394:17.2":"lokanatham narasabham; ","tha-ap394:17.3":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap394:17.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap394:18.1":"‘Ime tini sata vira, ","tha-ap394:18.2":"Purisa ekato gana; ","tha-ap394:18.3":"Upatthanasalam sukatam, ","tha-ap394:18.4":"Niyyadenti tuvam muni. ","tha-ap394:19.1":"Bhikkhusanghassa purato, ","tha-ap394:19.2":"sampaticchitva cakkhuma’; ","tha-ap394:19.3":"Tinnam satanam purato, ","tha-ap394:19.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap394:20.1":"‘Tisatapi ca jettho ca, ","tha-ap394:20.2":"anuvattimsu ekato; ","tha-ap394:20.3":"Sampattinhi karitvana, ","tha-ap394:20.4":"sabbe anubhavissatha. ","tha-ap394:21.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap394:21.2":"sitibhavamanuttaram; ","tha-ap394:21.3":"Ajaram amatam santam, ","tha-ap394:21.4":"nibbanam phassayissatha’. ","tha-ap394:22.1":"Evam buddho viyakasi, ","tha-ap394:22.2":"sabbannu samanuttaro; ","tha-ap394:22.3":"Buddhassa vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap394:22.4":"somanassam pavedayim. ","tha-ap394:23.1":"Timsa kappasahassani, ","tha-ap394:23.2":"devaloke ramim aham; ","tha-ap394:23.3":"Devadhipo pancasatam, ","tha-ap394:23.4":"devarajjamakarayim. ","tha-ap394:24.1":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap394:24.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap394:24.3":"Devarajjam karontassa, ","tha-ap394:24.4":"mahadeva avandisum. ","tha-ap394:25.1":"Idha manusake rajjam, ","tha-ap394:25.2":"parisa honti bandhava; ","tha-ap394:25.3":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap394:25.4":"vasettho nama brahmano. ","tha-ap394:26.1":"Asitikoti nicayo, ","tha-ap394:26.2":"tassa putto ahosaham; ","tha-ap394:26.3":"Selo iti mamam namam, ","tha-ap394:26.4":"chalange paramim gato. ","tha-ap394:27.1":"Janghaviharam vicaram, ","tha-ap394:27.2":"sasissehi purakkhato; ","tha-ap394:27.3":"Jatabharikabharitam, ","tha-ap394:27.4":"keniyam nama tapasam. ","tha-ap394:28.1":"Patiyattahutim disva, ","tha-ap394:28.2":"idam vacanamabravim; ","tha-ap394:28.3":"‘Avaho va vivaho va, ","tha-ap394:28.4":"raja va te nimantito’. ","tha-ap394:29.1":"‘Ahutim yitthukamoham, ","tha-ap394:29.2":"brahmane devasammate; ","tha-ap394:29.3":"Na nimantemi rajanam, ","tha-ap394:29.4":"ahuti me na vijjati. ","tha-ap394:30.1":"Na catthi mayhamavaho, ","tha-ap394:30.2":"vivaho me na vijjati; ","tha-ap394:30.3":"Sakyanam nandijanano, ","tha-ap394:30.4":"settho loke sadevake. ","tha-ap394:31.1":"Sabbalokahitatthaya, ","tha-ap394:31.2":"sabbasattasukhavaho; ","tha-ap394:31.3":"So me nimantito ajja, ","tha-ap394:31.4":"tassetam patiyadanam. ","tha-ap394:32.1":"Timbarusakavannabho, ","tha-ap394:32.2":"appameyyo anupamo; ","tha-ap394:32.3":"Rupenasadiso buddho, ","tha-ap394:32.4":"svatanaya nimantito. ","tha-ap394:33.1":"Ukkamukhapahatthova, ","tha-ap394:33.2":"khadirangarasannibho; ","tha-ap394:33.3":"Vijjupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:33.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:34.1":"Pabbatagge yatha acci, ","tha-ap394:34.2":"punnamayeva candima; ","tha-ap394:34.3":"Nalaggivannasankaso, ","tha-ap394:34.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:35.1":"Asambhito bhayatito, ","tha-ap394:35.2":"bhavantakarano muni; ","tha-ap394:35.3":"Sihupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:35.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:36.1":"Kusalo buddhadhammehi, ","tha-ap394:36.2":"apasayho parehi so; ","tha-ap394:36.3":"Nagupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:36.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:37.1":"Saddhammacarakusalo, ","tha-ap394:37.2":"buddhanago asadiso; ","tha-ap394:37.3":"Usabhupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:37.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:38.1":"Anantavanno amitayaso, ","tha-ap394:38.2":"Vicittasabbalakkhano; ","tha-ap394:38.3":"Sakkupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:38.4":"So me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:39.1":"Vasi gani patapi ca, ","tha-ap394:39.2":"tejassi ca durasado; ","tha-ap394:39.3":"Brahmupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:39.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:40.1":"Pattadhammo dasabalo, ","tha-ap394:40.2":"balatibalaparago; ","tha-ap394:40.3":"Dharanupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:40.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:41.1":"Silavicisamakinno, ","tha-ap394:41.2":"dhammavinnanakhobhito; ","tha-ap394:41.3":"Udadhupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:41.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:42.1":"Durasado duppasaho, ","tha-ap394:42.2":"acalo uggato braha; ","tha-ap394:42.3":"Nerupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:42.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:43.1":"Anantanano asamasamo, ","tha-ap394:43.2":"Atulo aggatam gato; ","tha-ap394:43.3":"Gaganupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:43.4":"So me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:44.1":"Pannarasamam bhanavaram. ","tha-ap394:45.1":"Patittha bhayabhitanam, ","tha-ap394:45.2":"tano saranagaminam; ","tha-ap394:45.3":"Assasako mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:45.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:46.1":"Asayo buddhimantanam, ","tha-ap394:46.2":"punnakkhettam sukhesinam; ","tha-ap394:46.3":"Ratanakaro mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:46.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:47.1":"Assasako vedakaro, ","tha-ap394:47.2":"samannaphaladayako; ","tha-ap394:47.3":"Meghupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:47.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:48.1":"Lokacakkhu mahatejo, ","tha-ap394:48.2":"sabbatamavinodano; ","tha-ap394:48.3":"Suriyupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:48.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:49.1":"Arammanavimuttisu, ","tha-ap394:49.2":"sabhavadassano muni; ","tha-ap394:49.3":"Candupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:49.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:50.1":"Buddho samussito loke, ","tha-ap394:50.2":"lakkhanehi alankato; ","tha-ap394:50.3":"Appameyyo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:50.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:51.1":"Yassa nanam appameyyam, ","tha-ap394:51.2":"silam yassa anupamam; ","tha-ap394:51.3":"Vimutti asadisa yassa, ","tha-ap394:51.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:52.1":"Yassa dhiti asadisa, ","tha-ap394:52.2":"thamo yassa acintiyo; ","tha-ap394:52.3":"Yassa parakkamo jettho, ","tha-ap394:52.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:53.1":"Rago doso ca moho ca, ","tha-ap394:53.2":"visa sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap394:53.3":"Agadupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:53.4":"so me buddho nimantito. ","tha-ap394:54.1":"Klesabyadhibahudukkha, ","tha-ap394:54.2":"sabbatamavinodano; ","tha-ap394:54.3":"Vejjupamo mahaviro, ","tha-ap394:54.4":"so me buddho nimantito’. ","tha-ap394:55.1":"Buddhoti bho yam vadesi, ","tha-ap394:55.2":"ghosopeso sudullabho; ","tha-ap394:55.3":"Buddho buddhoti sutvana, ","tha-ap394:55.4":"piti me udapajjatha. ","tha-ap394:56.1":"Abbhantaram aganhantam, ","tha-ap394:56.2":"piti me bahi nicchare; ","tha-ap394:56.3":"Soham pitimano santo, ","tha-ap394:56.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap394:57.1":"‘Kaham nu kho so bhagava, ","tha-ap394:57.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap394:57.3":"Tattha gantva namassissam, ","tha-ap394:57.4":"samannaphaladayakam. ","tha-ap394:58.1":"Paggayha dakkhinam bahum, ","tha-ap394:58.2":"vedajato katanjali; ","tha-ap394:58.3":"Acikkhi me dhammarajam, ","tha-ap394:58.4":"sokasallavinodanam’. ","tha-ap394:59.1":"‘Udentamva mahamegham, ","tha-ap394:59.2":"nilam anjanasannibham; ","tha-ap394:59.3":"Sagaram viya dissantam, ","tha-ap394:59.4":"passasetam mahavanam. ","tha-ap394:60.1":"Ettha so vasate buddho, ","tha-ap394:60.2":"adantadamako muni; ","tha-ap394:60.3":"Vinayanto ca veneyye, ","tha-ap394:60.4":"bodhento bodhipakkhiye’. ","tha-ap394:61.1":"Pipasitova udakam, ","tha-ap394:61.2":"bhojanamva jighacchito; ","tha-ap394:61.3":"Gavi yatha vacchagiddha, ","tha-ap394:61.4":"evaham vicinim jinam. ","tha-ap394:62.1":"Acaraupacarannu, ","tha-ap394:62.2":"dhammanucchavisamvaram; ","tha-ap394:62.3":"Sikkhapemi sake sisse, ","tha-ap394:62.4":"gacchante jinasantikam. ","tha-ap394:63.1":"‘Durasada bhagavanto, ","tha-ap394:63.2":"sihava ekacarino; ","tha-ap394:63.3":"Pade padam nikkhipanta, ","tha-ap394:63.4":"agaccheyyatha manava. ","tha-ap394:64.1":"Asiviso yatha ghoro, ","tha-ap394:64.2":"migarajava kesari; ","tha-ap394:64.3":"Mattova kunjaro danti, ","tha-ap394:64.4":"evam buddha durasada. ","tha-ap394:65.1":"Ukkasitanca khipitam, ","tha-ap394:65.2":"ajjhupekkhiya manava; ","tha-ap394:65.3":"Pade padam nikkhipanta, ","tha-ap394:65.4":"upetha buddhasantikam. ","tha-ap394:66.1":"Patisallanagaruka, ","tha-ap394:66.2":"appasadda durasada; ","tha-ap394:66.3":"Durupasankama buddha, ","tha-ap394:66.4":"garu honti sadevake. ","tha-ap394:67.1":"Yadaham panham pucchami, ","tha-ap394:67.2":"patisammodayami va; ","tha-ap394:67.3":"Appasadda tada hotha, ","tha-ap394:67.4":"munibhutava titthatha. ","tha-ap394:68.1":"Yam so deseti sambuddho, ","tha-ap394:68.2":"khemam nibbanapattiya; ","tha-ap394:68.3":"Tamevattham nisametha, ","tha-ap394:68.4":"saddhammasavanam sukham’. ","tha-ap394:69.1":"Upasankamma sambuddham, ","tha-ap394:69.2":"sammodim munina aham; ","tha-ap394:69.3":"Tam katham vitisaretva, ","tha-ap394:69.4":"lakkhane upadharayim. ","tha-ap394:70.1":"Lakkhane dve ca kankhami, ","tha-ap394:70.2":"passami timsalakkhane; ","tha-ap394:70.3":"Kosohitavatthaguyham, ","tha-ap394:70.4":"iddhiya dassayi muni. ","tha-ap394:71.1":"Jivham ninnamayitvana, ","tha-ap394:71.2":"kannasote ca nasike; ","tha-ap394:71.3":"Patimasi nalatantam, ","tha-ap394:71.4":"kevalam chadayi jino. ","tha-ap394:72.1":"Tassaham lakkhane disva, ","tha-ap394:72.2":"paripunne sabyanjane; ","tha-ap394:72.3":"Buddhoti nittham gantvana, ","tha-ap394:72.4":"saha sissehi pabbajim. ","tha-ap394:73.1":"Satehi tihi sahito, ","tha-ap394:73.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap394:73.3":"Addhamase asampatte, ","tha-ap394:73.4":"sabbe pattamha nibbutim. ","tha-ap394:74.1":"Ekato kammam katvana, ","tha-ap394:74.2":"punnakkhette anuttare; ","tha-ap394:74.3":"Ekato samsaritvana, ","tha-ap394:74.4":"ekato vinivattayum. ","tha-ap394:75.1":"Gopanasiyo datvana, ","tha-ap394:75.2":"pugadhamme vasim aham; ","tha-ap394:75.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap394:75.4":"attha hetu labhamaham. ","tha-ap394:76.1":"Disasu pujito homi, ","tha-ap394:76.2":"bhoga ca amita mama; ","tha-ap394:76.3":"Patittha homi sabbesam, ","tha-ap394:76.4":"taso mama na vijjati. ","tha-ap394:77.1":"Byadhayo me na vijjanti, ","tha-ap394:77.2":"dighayum palayami ca; ","tha-ap394:77.3":"Sukhumacchaviko homi, ","tha-ap394:77.4":"avase patthite vase. ","tha-ap394:78.1":"Attha gopanasi datva, ","tha-ap394:78.2":"pugadhamme vasim aham; ","tha-ap394:78.3":"Patisambhidarahattanca, ","tha-ap394:78.4":"etam me aparatthamam. ","tha-ap394:79.1":"Sabbavositavosano, ","tha-ap394:79.2":"katakicco anasavo; ","tha-ap394:79.3":"Atthagopanasi nama, ","tha-ap394:79.4":"tava putto mahamuni. ","tha-ap394:80.1":"Panca thambhani datvana, ","tha-ap394:80.2":"pugadhamme vasim aham; ","tha-ap394:80.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap394:80.4":"panca hetu labhamaham. ","tha-ap394:81.1":"Acalo homi mettaya, ","tha-ap394:81.2":"anunango bhavamaham; ","tha-ap394:81.3":"Adeyyavacano homi, ","tha-ap394:81.4":"na dhamsemi yatha aham. ","tha-ap394:82.1":"Abhantam hoti me cittam, ","tha-ap394:82.2":"akhilo homi kassaci; ","tha-ap394:82.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap394:82.4":"vimalo homi sasane. ","tha-ap394:83.1":"Sagaravo sappatisso, ","tha-ap394:83.2":"katakicco anasavo; ","tha-ap394:83.3":"Savako te mahavira, ","tha-ap394:83.4":"bhikkhu tam vandate muni. ","tha-ap394:84.1":"Katva sukatapallankam, ","tha-ap394:84.2":"salayam pannapesaham; ","tha-ap394:84.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap394:84.4":"panca hetu labhamaham. ","tha-ap394:85.1":"Ucce kule pajayitva, ","tha-ap394:85.2":"mahabhogo bhavamaham; ","tha-ap394:85.3":"Sabbasampattiko homi, ","tha-ap394:85.4":"maccheram me na vijjati. ","tha-ap394:86.1":"Gamane patthite mayham, ","tha-ap394:86.2":"pallanko upatitthati; ","tha-ap394:86.3":"Saha pallankasetthena, ","tha-ap394:86.4":"gacchami mama patthitam. ","tha-ap394:87.1":"Tena pallankadanena, ","tha-ap394:87.2":"tamam sabbam vinodayim; ","tha-ap394:87.3":"Sabbabhinnabalappatto, ","tha-ap394:87.4":"thero vandati tam muni. ","tha-ap394:88.1":"Parakiccattakiccani, ","tha-ap394:88.2":"sabbakiccani sadhayim; ","tha-ap394:88.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap394:88.4":"pavisim abhayam puram. ","tha-ap394:89.1":"Parinitthitasalamhi, ","tha-ap394:89.2":"paribhogamadasaham; ","tha-ap394:89.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap394:89.4":"setthattam ajjhupagato. ","tha-ap394:90.1":"Ye keci damaka loke, ","tha-ap394:90.2":"hatthiasse damenti ye; ","tha-ap394:90.3":"Karitva karana nana, ","tha-ap394:90.4":"darunena damenti te. ","tha-ap394:91.1":"Na hevam tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap394:91.2":"damesi naranariyo; ","tha-ap394:91.3":"Adandena asatthena, ","tha-ap394:91.4":"damesi uttame dame. ","tha-ap394:92.1":"Danassa vanne kittento, ","tha-ap394:92.2":"desanakusalo muni; ","tha-ap394:92.3":"Ekapanham kathentova, ","tha-ap394:92.4":"bodhesi tisate muni. ","tha-ap394:93.1":"Danta mayam sarathina, ","tha-ap394:93.2":"suvimutta anasava; ","tha-ap394:93.3":"Sabbabhinnabalapatta, ","tha-ap394:93.4":"nibbuta upadhikkhaye. ","tha-ap394:94.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap394:94.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap394:94.3":"Atikkanta bhaya sabbe, ","tha-ap394:94.4":"saladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap394:95.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap394:95.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap394:95.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap394:96.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap394:96.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap394:96.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap394:97.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap394:97.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap394:97.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap394:98.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma selo sapariso bhagavato santike ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap394:99.1":"Selattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}